cc:Work.dc:title: Farmer and Pumpkinhead
cc:Work.dc:description: A farmer looks down on a pumpkin that is a head. This odd cartoon was from a political cartoon from 1897. Some drab politics of the day that is lost on most modern people I suppose. But no one can argue with the timelessness of a melting pumpkinhead and a farmer with a pitchfork. Beautiful!
